data.description: NEW PHOTOS! Welcome to 1401 Louisiana Ave, your dream home come true! This charming two-bedroom, two-bath property sits on a beautiful fenced corner lot with lush landscaping and a welcoming circle driveway. As you enter the home, you'll immediately notice the stunning luxury vinyl planking that stretches throughout the main living, dining, and bedrooms. The fresh interior paint and new baseboards create a seamless flow, while the updated light fixtures add a touch of modern elegance. The primary suite is a true oasis, featuring a spacious walk-in closet and a luxurious en-suite bathroom with a jetted bathtub. The second bedroom is inviting, with plenty of natural light and ample closet space. The heart of the home is the gourmet kitchen, boasting custom wood cabinets with beautiful backlighting, updated appliances, and plenty of counter space for all your cooking needs. Other updates to the home include energy-efficient windows and a relocated washer/dryer hookup from the kitchen to the garage with updated electrical and plumbing. 1401 Louisiana is an ideal location, just two miles from the East Lake Toho Marina Park and the vibrant Historic Downtown District of St. Cloud. There are plenty of restaurants and shopping centers nearby. This unique home has a spacious backyard perfect for entertaining and relaxing and an architectural style that exudes charm and character. Don't miss your chance to make this stunning property your new home sweet home!
